






























































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































/* 基础样式 */
.container.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100vh;
  background-color: #f2f2f2;
  font-size: 28rpx;
}
/* 导航栏 */
.nav-bar.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 20rpx;
  background-color: #fff;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
}
.nav-left.data-v-c09e99b4,
.nav-right.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  width: 120rpx;
}
.nav-title.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  font-size: 32rpx;
  font-weight: bold;
}
/* 标签栏 */
.tab-container.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  background-color: #fff;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
}
.tab-scroll.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.tab-list.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  display: flex;
  padding: 0 20rpx;
}
.tab-item.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  padding: 20rpx 30rpx;
  border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
}
.tab-item.active.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  border-bottom: 3px solid #007aff;
}
.tab-item.active text.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  color: #007aff;
  font-weight: bold;
}
/* 内容区域 */
.content-scroll.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  height: calc(100vh - 140rpx);
}
.content.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  padding: 20rpx;
}
/* 模块样式 */
.module.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  background-color: #fff;
  padding: 20rpx;
  border-radius: 8rpx;
  margin-bottom: 20rpx;
}
.module-title.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  font-size: 32rpx;
  font-weight: bold;
  margin-bottom: 20rpx;
  padding-bottom: 10rpx;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
}
/* 数据组 */
.data-group.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  margin-bottom: 30rpx;
}
.group-title.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  font-size: 28rpx;
  font-weight: bold;
  margin-bottom: 15rpx;
  color: #666;
}
/* 数据网格 */
.data-grid.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 15rpx;
}
.grid-item.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  width: calc(33.333% - 10rpx);
  background-color: #f9f9f9;
  padding: 15rpx;
  border-radius: 4rpx;
}
.item-label.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  font-size: 24rpx;
  color: #666;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 5rpx;
}
.item-value.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  font-size: 26rpx;
  color: #333;
  font-weight: bold;
}
/* 光伏状态按钮样式 - 核心修复 */
.status-row.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  display: flex;
  gap: 10rpx; /* 统一间距 */
  margin-bottom: 15rpx;
}
/* 4个按钮的行 */
.status-row-4.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  justify-content: space-between;
}
/* 2个按钮的行 */
.status-row-2.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  justify-content: flex-start;
}
.status-btn.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  height: 80rpx;
  border-radius: 8rpx; /* 统一圆角，贴合设计图 */
  border: 2rpx solid #ddd;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  background-color: #fff;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
  /* 固定按钮最小宽度，避免拉伸变形 */
  min-width: 140rpx;
  /* 按数量分配宽度 */
  flex: 1;
  max-width: calc(25% - 7.5rpx); /* 4个按钮时的最大宽度 */
}
/* 2个按钮时的宽度调整 */
.status-row-2 .status-btn.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  max-width: calc(50% - 5rpx);
}
.status-btn.active.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  background-color: #007aff;
  border-color: #007aff;
}
.status-btn-text.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  font-size: 26rpx;
  color: #333;
}
.status-btn.active .status-btn-text.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  color: #fff;
  font-weight: bold;
}
/* 光伏参数两列布局 - 核心修复 */
.pv-params-grid.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 10rpx; /* 统一间距 */
}
.pv-param-item.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  width: calc(50% - 5rpx); /* 精准计算，避免间隙溢出 */
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 15rpx;
  background-color: #f9f9f9;
  border-radius: 4rpx;
  box-sizing: border-box; /* 避免padding撑大宽度 */
}
.pv-param-label.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  font-size: 24rpx;
  color: #666;
  flex: 1; /* 标签占比 */
}
.pv-param-value.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  font-size: 26rpx;
  color: #333;
  font-weight: bold;
  text-align: right; /* 数值右对齐，更整齐 */
  min-width: 80rpx; /* 数值最小宽度，避免抖动 */
}
/* 消防网格 */
.fire-grid.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 15rpx;
}
.fire-item.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  width: calc(50% - 7.5rpx);
  background-color: #f9f9f9;
  padding: 15rpx;
  border-radius: 4rpx;
}
.fire-title.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  font-size: 26rpx;
  font-weight: bold;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 10rpx;
  padding-bottom: 5rpx;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
}
.fire-detail.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  display: flex;
  margin-bottom: 8rpx;
  font-size: 24rpx;
}
.detail-label.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  color: #666;
  width: 120rpx;
}
.detail-value.data-v-c09e99b4 {
  color: #333;
  flex: 1;
}
/* 响应式适配 - 优化 */
@media (max-width: 750rpx) {
.grid-item.data-v-c09e99b4 {
    width: calc(50% - 7.5rpx);
}
.fire-item.data-v-c09e99b4 {
    width: 100%;
}

  /* 小屏时状态按钮自适应 */
.status-btn.data-v-c09e99b4 {
    min-width: 120rpx;
}
}
@media (max-width: 480rpx) {
.grid-item.data-v-c09e99b4 {
    width: 100%;
}
.status-row.data-v-c09e99b4 {
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.status-btn.data-v-c09e99b4 {
    width: calc(50% - 5rpx);
    max-width: none;
    margin-bottom: 10rpx;
}
.pv-param-item.data-v-c09e99b4 {
    width: 100%;
}
}

